'''Ousmane William Mbaye''' (yavutse 1952), yavukiye muri  [[Senegali|Senegal]] azwi mu gukora filimi <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/ousmane-william-mbaye/</ref>.  Mbaye azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa documentaire ''Mère-Bi'' ''ishimwa cyane'' na film Doomi Ngacc, ''Fresque'' na ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' .  Usibye gukora amafilime, ni numu producer mukuru, utunganya umurongo, umwanditsi wa sinema, producer wamahanga, umuyobozi wamafoto, uwandika amajwi, umuyobozi ushinzwe umusaruro, umwanditsi, na producer<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/ousmane-william-mbaye</ref><ref>https://www.etonnants-voyageurs.com/MBAYE-Ousmane-William.html</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1952 i [[Paris]], mu [[Bufaransa]]. Nyina, Annette Mbaye d'Erneville akomoka muri [[senegali]] <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/321371180_Ousmane_William_Mbaye_director_Kemtiyu_Cheikh_Anta_2016_94_minutes_Wolof_and_French_with_English_subtitles_Senegal_Les_Films_Mame_Yande_anf_Autoproduction_DVD_2000</ref>.  

== Umwuga ==
Mbaye yahuguye muri Conservatoire Libre du Cinéma Français (Konserwatori Yubusa ya Sinema y'Abafaransa). Nyuma yize muri kaminuza ya Paris 8 Vincennes-Saint-Denis aho yatangiriye gukina amashusho. Amaze kubona impamyabumenyi, yimukiye muri [[Senegali]] . Nyuma yaje kuba umuyobozi wungirije. Kuva 1990 kugeza 1997, yabaye umuhuzabikorwa nuwashinze Rencontres Cinématographiques ya Dakar (RECIDAK).<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/ousmane-william-mbaye</ref><ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=5633</ref><ref>https://new.in-24.com/News/70837.html</ref> 

Mu 1979, yakoze kandi ayobora filime ye ya mbere ya ''Doomi Ngacc'' <ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/william-ousmane-mbaye/5633</ref>. Mugufi yatsindiye Bronze Tanit mu iserukiramuco rya Filime ya Carthage . Kuva mu 2000, yatangiye gukora documentaire nka ''Président Dia'' na ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' .  Mu 2003, yakoze documentaire ngufi ''Xalima la plume'' yerekeye umucuranzi wa [[Senegali|Senegal]] Seydina Insa Wade. Nyuma yaho gato yatsindiye igihembo cya Documentaire muri Festival ya Milan<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=5633</ref> <ref>https://www.ma-mediatheque.net/Default/doc/SYRACUSE/568198/mentions-legales.aspx</ref>. Mu 2005, yayoboye documentaire ''Fer et verre'', yibanze ku muhanzi wa plastiki wo muri Senegal Anta Germane Gaye . Muri 2008, yakoze ''Mère-Bi'' ngufi, ishingiye kuri nyina.<ref>http://rwanda.spla.pro/en/file.film.xalima-la-plume.619.html</ref>  

Mu mwaka wa 2016, yakoze documentaire yerekana ubuzima bwa ''Kemtiyu, Cheikh Anta'' ivuga ku buzima bw’amateka ya Senegal, umuganga, n’umunyapolitiki Cheikh Anta Diop<ref>https://www.au-senegal.com/le-cineaste-ousmane-william-mbaye-integre-l-academie-des-oscars,15805.html</ref> .  Iyi filime yakiriwe neza n'abayinenga kandi yerekanwa mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime.   Yahawe igihembo cya EU / ACP mu iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO) 2017<ref>https://www.jcctunisie.org/jcc2017/eng/filmsDetail.php?id_film=34</ref>.<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/articles/review-of-kemtiyu-cheikh-anta/</ref> 

